         VERSION=1.3.12
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:db36be3d9035b4a8fcd238ff243358f298ab1dbe84ff1bc398166a0a885ce81507d341c250cfd0167b7d134010d0670e50f7f3c03d845626657cbc39cb76d2ae
